title: ShapeShift Settles SEC Charges It Sold Crypto Securities
description: The federal regulator instituted a cease-and-desist against ShapeShift, which dissolved its U.S. crypto exchange in 2021.

title: SEC Pushes Back Decision on BlackRock, Fidelity's Ether ETF Applications
description: The SEC wants to know if the applications for ETFs that hold Ethereum's ether (ETH) are supported by the same arguments that led to the approval of spot bitcoin ETFs.
